<details class="wp-block-details is-style-default" style="border-bottom-width:1px;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--md);padding-right:0;padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--md);padding-left:0"><summary>How to enter Pro license key?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
<p>After purchasing a Blockify Pro membership through LemonSqueezy, you will be provided with a unique license key in your LemonSqueezy order. Your license key can be entered on the Plugins page of your WordPress site dashboard. </p>
